---
// src/components/home/Hero.astro
---

<section
  id="inicio"
  class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- Decoración de fondo -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute -top-32 -right-32 w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full bg-primary/5 blur-3xl"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-px h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-outline-variant/30 to-transparent opacity-60"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-content mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-24 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Columna de texto -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-8">
        <!-- Etiqueta superior -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8 animate-fade-in">
          <span class="block w-8 h-px bg-primary"></span>
          <span
            class="font-mono text-xs text-primary uppercase tracking-widest"
          >
            Ingeniero de Software & Diseñador de Producto
          </span>
        </div>

        <!-- Heading principal -->
        <h1
          class="font-headline text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-on-surface animate-fade-up"
        >
          Construyendo el<br />
          <span class="text-primary">futuro digital</span><br />
          <span class="text-on-surface-variant font-normal italic"
            >con precisión técnica.</span
          >
        </h1>

        <!-- Descripción -->
        <p
          class="mt-8 max-w-xl text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-light animate-fade-up [animation-delay:150ms]"
        >
          Creo experiencias web de punta a punta — desde una interfaz cuidada
          hasta una arquitectura de servidor sólida. Me apasiona el código
          limpio y los productos que resuelven problemas reales.
        </p>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div
          class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 animate-fade-up [animation-delay:250ms]"
        >
          <a
            href="/#portafolio"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-on-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-md hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity duration-300"
          >
            Explorar Proyectos
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-4 h-4"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/#sobre-mi"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-surface-high text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-surface-highest transition-colors duration-300"
          >
            Mi Historia
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Columna decorativa derecha -->
      <div
        class="hidden lg:flex lg:col-span-4 justify-end items-center animate-fade-in [animation-delay:300ms]"
      >
        <div class="relative w-64 h-64">
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full"
            style="border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--outline-variant) 20%, transparent);"
          >
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute inset-4 rounded-full"
            style="border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--outline-variant) 10%, transparent);"
          >
          </div>

          <!-- Foto -->
          <div
            class="absolute inset-8 rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-surface-container"
          >
            <img
              src="/profile.jpg"
              alt="Luis Gutierrez"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="eager"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Etiqueta flotante -->
          <div
            class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-surface-container rounded-xl px-4 py-2 ghost-border"
          >
            <p
              class="font-mono text-2xs text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider"
            >
              Disponible
            </p>
            <p class="font-body text-xs font-medium text-on-surface">
              Para proyectos
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div
      class="mt-20 pt-10 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 animate-fade-up [animation-delay:400ms]"
      style="border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--outline-variant) 30%, transparent);"
    >
      {
        [
          { value: "3+", label: "Años de experiencia" },
          { value: "20+", label: "Proyectos completados" },
          { value: "100%", label: "Compromiso" },
        ].map(({ value, label }) => (
          <div>
            <p class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold text-on-surface">
              {value}
            </p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">{label}</p>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
